<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>.. فَأَكْثَرُ أَهْلُ النَّارِ هُمْ حَقِيقَةً<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>رَوَيْنَا حَدِيثًا فِيهِ صِدْقًا مُصَدَّقَا<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>تََُخِّلي التَّبَاهِي تُبْدلُ اللَّهْوَ بِالْبُكَا<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>وَتَبْذُلُ كُلَّ الْجُهْدِ بِالزُّهْدِ وَالتُّقَى<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>وَتَعْتَاضُ عَنْ لِينٍ خُشُونَةً<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>وَعَنْ يَابِسٍ فِي الدِّينِ أَخْضَرَ مُورِقَا<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>رَعَى اللهُ نِسْوَنًا تَبِيتُ قَوَاتِنًا<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>وَيُصْبِحُ مِنْهَا الْقَلْبُ بِالْخَوْفِ مُحْرِقَا<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>تَظِلُّ عَنْ الْمَرْعَى الْخَصِيبِ صَوَائِمًا<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>وَيُمْسِي سَمِينُ الْبَطْنِ بِالظَّهْرِ مُلْصَقَا<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>تَرَى بَيْنَ عَيْنٍ وَالسُّهَادِ تَوَاصًلاً<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>وَبَيْنَ الْكَرَى وَالْعَيْنِ مِنْهَا تَفَرُّقَا<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>وَبَيْنَ مِعَاءٍ وَالْغِذَاءِ تَقَاطُعًا<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>وَبَيْنَ خُلُوفِ الْمِسْكِ وَالثَّغْرِ مُلْتَقَى<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span>تَرَى نَاحِلاتٍ قَارِئَاتٍ مَصَاحِفًا<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span>وَلُؤْلُؤُ بَحْرِ الدُّرِّ فِي الْوَرْدِ مُشْرِقَا<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span>فَدَتْهَا مِن الآفَاتِ كُلُّ نُفُوسِ مَنْ<a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p18"></span>يُخَالِفُهَا فِي الْوَصْفِ غَرْبًا وَمَشْرِقَا<a href="#p18" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p19"></span>خَلِيلِي إِنَّ الْمَوْتَ لا شَكَّ نَازِلٌ<a href="#p19" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p20"></span>وَبَيْنَ الأَحِبَّا لا يَزَالُ مُفَرِّقَا ... &gt;?<a href="#p20" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
